perception_module.prompt:
Analyze this Pokemon Red game state and extract key information.

Input: {textual_representation}

Return JSON with this structure:
{
  "player_info": {
    "name": "player_name",
    "money": amount,
    "badges": ["badge_list"]
  },
  "location_info": {
    "current_location": "location_name",
    "coordinates": {"x": x, "y": y},
    "valid_moves": ["directions"]
  },
  "pokemon_party": [
    {
      "species": "pokemon_name",
      "level": level,
      "current_hp": hp,
      "max_hp": max_hp,
      "status": "condition"
    }
  ],
  "inventory": [
    {"item": "item_name", "quantity": count}
  ],
  "dialog_text": "current_dialog_or_null",
  "game_state_type": "overworld|dialog|menu|battle|title"
}

Extract this information accurately from the game state.
